# 强制 Markdown 识别并禁用其他检测
*.md linguist-language=Markdown
*.md linguist-documentation=false

# 如果有以数字结尾的 .md 文件（容易被误认为 man page）
*.1.md linguist-language=Markdown
*.2.md linguist-language=Markdown
*.3.md linguist-language=Markdown
*.4.md linguist-language=Markdown
*.5.md linguist-language=Markdown
*.6.md linguist-language=Markdown
*.7.md linguist-language=Markdown
*.8.md linguist-language=Markdown
*.9.md linguist-language=Markdown